2026-06-01T11:08:18.3788805Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-06-01T11:08:18.3789566Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-06-01T11:08:18.3790304Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-06-01T11:08:18.3791207Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-06-01T11:08:18.3791960Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-06-01T11:08:18.3792736Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-06-01T11:08:18.3793459Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-06-01T11:08:18.3794174Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
