2026-06-01T11:08:18.4441491Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-06-01T11:08:18.4442531Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-06-01T11:08:18.4443314Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-06-01T11:08:18.4444207Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-06-01T11:08:18.4445052Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-06-01T11:08:18.4445837Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-06-01T11:08:18.4446524Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
